results_vt = pd.DataFrame()
results_fts = pd.DataFrame()
results_ftw = pd.DataFrame()

aoi_list = ['Design District', 'Gold Coast', 'Fulton Market', 'Williamsburg', 'Newbury']

aois = ['Newbury']


for proj in tqdm((wejo), total=len(wejo)):
    projects = GoProject(proj)
    results_wejo = projects.get_vehicle_traffic_results() #target_aois = aois
    df = results_wejo.get_timeseries('uznorm.count', form='long')
    results_vt = results_vt.append(df, ignore_index=True)


for proj in tqdm((spectus), total=len(spectus)):
    projects = GoProject(proj)
    results_spectus = projects.get_foot_traffic_results() #target_aois = aois
    df = results_spectus.get_timeseries('uznorm.count', form='long')
    results_fts = results_fts.append(df, ignore_index=True)
